json.query: SELECT  "学生姓名","学生系统账号","学生id","服务商姓名","服务商id","校董姓名","校董id","大赛状态","teamname","日期" FROM (select  student_name as "学生姓名" ,system_login_name as "学生系统账号" ,student_id as "学生id" ,user_name as "服务商姓名" ,agent_id as "服务商id" ,level1_username as "校董姓名" ,levle1_agentid as "校董id" ,state as "大赛状态" ,teamname ,dt as "日期" from hive.dwd.dwd_etp_race_status where dt>='2020-10-19' and dt<='2020-10-19') T GROUP BY "学生姓名","学生系统账号","学生id","服务商姓名","服务商id","校董姓名","校董id","大赛状态","teamname","日期"

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT "校董id", "校董名称", "服务商id", "服务商名称", sum("付费用户数") AS "sum(付费用户数)", sum("参加ETP大赛用户数") AS "sum(参加ETP大赛用户数)", sum("参与率") AS "sum(参与率)" FROM (SELECT a.level1_agentid AS "校董id", a.level1_username AS "校董名称", a.agent_id AS "服务商id", a.username AS "服务商名称", count(*) AS "付费用户数", count(CASE WHEN p.studentId IS NOT NULL THEN p.studentId END) AS "参加ETP大赛用户数", count(CASE WHEN p.studentId IS NOT NULL THEN p.studentId END) / count(*) AS "参与率" FROM (SELECT a.level1_agentid, a.level1_username, a.agent_id, a.username, s.student_Id FROM (SELECT * FROM hive.dwd.dwd_agent_level_new WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) a LEFT JOIN (SELECT CAST(extral_agent_id AS bigint) AS extral_agent_id, student_id FROM hive.dwd.dwd_st_student_basic_info WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d') AND source = 1 AND extral_payment_time IS NOT NULL) s ON a.agent_id = s.extral_agent_id) a LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d') AND teamStatus = 1) p ON a.student_Id = p.studentId GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4) T GROUP BY "校董id", "校董名称", "服务商id", "服务商名称") CT

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT "学生姓名", "学生系统账号", "学生id", "服务商姓名", "服务商id", "校董姓名", "校董id", "大赛状态", "teamname", "日期" FROM (SELECT student_name AS "学生姓名", system_login_name AS "学生系统账号", student_id AS "学生id", user_name AS "服务商姓名", agent_id AS "服务商id", level1_username AS "校董姓名", levle1_agentid AS "校董id", state AS "大赛状态", teamname, dt AS "日期" FROM hive.dwd.dwd_etp_race_status WHERE dt >= '2020-10-19' AND dt <= '2020-10-19') T GROUP BY "学生姓名", "学生系统账号", "学生id", "服务商姓名", "服务商id", "校董姓名", "校董id", "大赛状态", "teamname", "日期") CT

SELECT  "校董id","校董姓名","服务商id","服务商姓名" ,  sum("团队人数") AS "sum(团队人数)",sum("参与ETP人数") AS "sum(参与ETP人数)",sum("报名成功人数") AS "sum(报名成功人数)",sum("一人组队") AS "sum(一人组队)",sum("二人组队") AS "sum(二人组队)",sum("三人组队") AS "sum(三人组队)" FROM (select a.level1_agentid as "校董id" ,a.level1_username as "校董姓名" ,a.agent_id as "服务商id" ,a.username as "服务商姓名" ,count(a.student_id) as "团队人数" ,count(t2.studentId) as "参与ETP人数" ,count(case when t2.registrationStatus=1 then t2.studentId end ) as "报名成功人数" ,count(case when t4.num=1 then t4.studentId end ) as "一人组队" ,count(case when t4.num=2 then t4.studentId end ) as "二人组队" ,count(case when t4.num=3 then t4.studentId end ) as "三人组队" from( select t.*,t1.student_id from(  	select * 	from hive.dwd.dwd_agent_level_new  	where dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	)t left join(  	select cast(extral_agent_id as bigint) as agent_id,student_id 	from hive.dwd.dwd_st_student_basic_info 	where dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	and source = 1 	and extral_payment_time is not null 	)t1  on t.agent_id=t1.agent_id  )a left join ( 	select * 	from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player  	where dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	) t2  on t2.studentId=a.student_id left join ( 	select t3.studentId,t4.num 	from( 		select * 		from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player  		where dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	) t3 left join ( 	select teamId,count(studentId) as num 	from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player 	where registrationStatus=1 	and dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	group by 1 	)t4  on t3.teamId=t4.teamId )t4  on a.student_id=t4.studentId group by 1,2,3,4 having count(a.student_id)<>0) T GROUP BY "校董id","校董姓名","服务商id","服务商姓名"

SELECT  "队伍人数","报名情况" ,  sum("队伍数量") AS "sum(队伍数量)",sum("学生数量") AS "sum(学生数量)" FROM (select  team_sum as "队伍人数" ,type as "报名情况" ,team_num as "队伍数量" ,num * jishu as "学生数量" from(select 	case when num>10 then 0 else num end as team_sum  	,'报名成功' as type  	,count(teamid) as team_num 	,case when count(teamid)=0 then 1 else count(teamid) end as  jishu 	,a.num as num from( 	select  		teamId 		,count(studentId) as num 	from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player 	where registrationStatus=1 	and dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	group by 1 	)a group by 1,5 )b UNION select 	team_sum as "队伍人数" 	,type as "报名情况" 	,team_num as "队伍数量" 	,num * jishu as "学生数量" from( select 	case when num>10 then 0 else num end as team_sum 	,'未报名成功' as type  	,count(teamid) as team_num 	,case when count(teamid)=0 then 1 else count(teamid) end  as jishu 	,a.num as num from( 	select  		teamId 		,count(studentId) as num 	from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player 	where registrationStatus=0 	and dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	group by 1 )a group by 1,5 )b order by 1) T GROUP BY "队伍人数","报名情况" ORDER BY "队伍人数" asc

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT "校董id", "校董姓名", "服务商id", "服务商姓名", sum("团队人数") AS "sum(团队人数)", sum("参与ETP人数") AS "sum(参与ETP人数)", sum("报名成功人数") AS "sum(报名成功人数)", sum("一人组队") AS "sum(一人组队)", sum("二人组队") AS "sum(二人组队)", sum("三人组队") AS "sum(三人组队)" FROM (SELECT a.level1_agentid AS "校董id", a.level1_username AS "校董姓名", a.agent_id AS "服务商id", a.username AS "服务商姓名", count(a.student_id) AS "团队人数", count(t2.studentId) AS "参与ETP人数", count(CASE WHEN t2.registrationStatus = 1 THEN t2.studentId END) AS "报名成功人数", count(CASE WHEN t4.num = 1 THEN t4.studentId END) AS "一人组队", count(CASE WHEN t4.num = 2 THEN t4.studentId END) AS "二人组队", count(CASE WHEN t4.num = 3 THEN t4.studentId END) AS "三人组队" FROM (SELECT t.*, t1.student_id FROM (SELECT * FROM hive.dwd.dwd_agent_level_new WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t LEFT JOIN (SELECT CAST(extral_agent_id AS bigint) AS agent_id, student_id FROM hive.dwd.dwd_st_student_basic_info WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d') AND source = 1 AND extral_payment_time IS NOT NULL) t1 ON t.agent_id = t1.agent_id) a LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t2 ON t2.studentId = a.student_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT t3.studentId, t4.num FROM (SELECT * FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t3 LEFT JOIN (SELECT teamId, count(studentId) AS num FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player WHERE registrationStatus = 1 AND dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d') GROUP BY 1) t4 ON t3.teamId = t4.teamId) t4 ON a.student_id = t4.studentId GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4 HAVING count(a.student_id) <> 0) T GROUP BY "校董id", "校董姓名", "服务商id", "服务商姓名") CT

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT "战队积分数", "战队名称", "学生姓名", "学生报名区域(分)", "学生年龄", "学生系统账号", "代理商ID", "代理商爱优选ID", "代理商名称", "校董ID", "校董名称", "累计推书单词总数", "累计推书单词正确总数", "活跃天数", "进入比赛页面活跃天数", "累计阅读天数", "头像连接", "总场数", "胜场数", "累计活跃时长(分)", "累计阅读单词数", "学生电话", "代理商电话" FROM (SELECT student_name AS "学生姓名", active_min AS "累计活跃时长(分)", areaname AS "学生报名区域(分)", age AS "学生年龄", phone AS "学生电话", system_login_name AS "学生系统账号", teamname AS "战队名称", agent_id AS "代理商ID", ag_ayx_id AS "代理商爱优选ID", agent_name AS "代理商名称", agent_phone AS "代理商电话", school_manager_id AS "校董ID", school_manager_ayx_id AS "校董爱优选ID", school_manager AS "校董名称", school_manager_phone AS "校董电话", totalwordnum AS "累计推书单词总数", findwordnum AS "累计推书单词正确总数", CAST(score AS int) AS "战队积分数", read_day AS "活跃天数", count_day AS "进入比赛页面活跃天数", read_second AS "当日有效阅读时长(分)", skill_id AS "功力值", read_day AS "累计阅读天数", maxContinueReadDay AS "连续阅读最大天数", headerPic AS "头像连接", battlecount AS "总场数", wincount AS "胜场数", readwordnum AS "累计阅读单词数" FROM hive.app_investment.app_etp_detail WHERE dt = '2020-10-20' ORDER BY CAST(score AS int) DESC, teamname DESC) T GROUP BY "战队积分数", "战队名称", "学生姓名", "学生报名区域(分)", "学生年龄", "学生系统账号", "代理商ID", "代理商爱优选ID", "代理商名称", "校董ID", "校董名称", "累计推书单词总数", "累计推书单词正确总数", "活跃天数", "进入比赛页面活跃天数", "累计阅读天数", "头像连接", "总场数", "胜场数", "累计活跃时长(分)", "累计阅读单词数", "学生电话", "代理商电话") CT

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT "注册填写省份", "付费用户数", "ETP大赛报名未成功用户数", "ETP大赛报名成功未组队用户数" FROM (SELECT t.studentProvinceName AS "注册填写省份", count(s.student_id) AS "付费用户数", count(CASE WHEN t2.registrationStatus <> 1 THEN t2.studentId END) AS "ETP大赛报名未成功用户数", count(CASE WHEN t2.registrationStatus = 1 AND t2.teamStatus = 0 THEN t2.studentId END) AS "ETP大赛报名成功未组队用户数" FROM (SELECT * FROM hive.dwd.dwd_st_student_basic_info WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d') AND source = 1 AND extral_payment_time IS NOT NULL) s INNER JOIN (SELECT * FROM hive.ods_english_agent.ods_ag_apply_account WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t ON s.student_id = t.studentId LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t2 ON s.student_id = t2.studentId GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 2 DESC) T GROUP BY "注册填写省份", "付费用户数", "ETP大赛报名未成功用户数", "ETP大赛报名成功未组队用户数") CT

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT "队伍PK总场次", sum("队伍数量") AS "sum(队伍数量)", sum("用户数量") AS "sum(用户数量)" FROM (SELECT battleCount AS "队伍PK总场次", count(DISTINCT teamId) AS "队伍数量", count(DISTINCT teamId) * 3 AS "用户数量" FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_team t WHERE isValid = 1 AND studentCount = 3 AND dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d') GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1 DESC) T GROUP BY "队伍PK总场次") CT

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT "队伍PK总场次", sum("队伍数量") AS "sum(队伍数量)", sum("用户数量") AS "sum(用户数量)" FROM (SELECT battleCount AS "队伍PK总场次", count(DISTINCT teamId) AS "队伍数量", count(DISTINCT teamId) * 3 AS "用户数量" FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_team t WHERE isValid = 1 AND studentCount = 3 AND dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d') GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1 DESC) T GROUP BY "队伍PK总场次") CT

SELECT  "队伍PK总场次" ,  sum("队伍数量") AS "sum(队伍数量)",sum("用户数量") AS "sum(用户数量)" FROM (select  battleCount as "队伍PK总场次" ,count(distinct teamId) as "队伍数量" ,count(distinct teamId)*3 as "用户数量" from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_team t  where isValid =1  and studentCount=3 and dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') group by 1 order by 1 desc) T GROUP BY "队伍PK总场次"

SELECT  "队伍PK总场次" ,  sum("队伍数量") AS "sum(队伍数量)",sum("用户数量") AS "sum(用户数量)" FROM (select  battleCount as "队伍PK总场次" ,count(distinct teamId) as "队伍数量" ,count(distinct teamId)*3 as "用户数量" from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_team t  where isValid =1  and studentCount=3 and dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') group by 1 order by 1 desc) T GROUP BY "队伍PK总场次"

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM (SELECT "校董id", "校董姓名", "服务商id", "服务商姓名", "学生姓名", "学生系统账号", "ETP大赛状态", "队伍名称" FROM (SELECT a.level1_agentid AS "校董id", a.level1_username AS "校董姓名", a.agent_id AS "服务商id", a.username AS "服务商姓名", a.student_name AS "学生姓名", a.system_login_name AS "学生系统账号", CASE WHEN t2.registrationStatus = 0 THEN '未报名成功' WHEN t2.registrationStatus = 1 AND t4.num IS NULL THEN '报名成功未组队' WHEN t4.num = 1 THEN '一人组队' WHEN t4.num = 2 THEN '二人组队' WHEN t4.num = 3 THEN '三人组队' END AS "ETP大赛状态", t4.teamName AS "队伍名称" FROM (SELECT t.*, t1.student_id, t1.student_name, t1.system_login_name FROM (SELECT * FROM hive.dwd.dwd_agent_level_new WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t LEFT JOIN (SELECT CAST(extral_agent_id AS bigint) AS agent_id, student_id, student_name, system_login_name FROM hive.dwd.dwd_st_student_basic_info WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d') AND source = 1 AND extral_payment_time IS NOT NULL) t1 ON t.agent_id = t1.agent_id) a INNER JOIN (SELECT * FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t2 ON t2.studentId = a.student_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT t3.studentId, t4.teamName, t4.num FROM (SELECT * FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t3 LEFT JOIN (SELECT p.teamId, t.teamName, count(studentId) AS num FROM (SELECT * FROM hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) p LEFT JOIN (SELECT * FROM ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_team WHERE dt = date_format(date_add('day', -1, current_timestamp), '%Y-%m-%d')) t ON p.teamId = t.teamId WHERE registrationStatus = 1 GROUP BY 1, 2) t4 ON t3.teamId = t4.teamId) t4 ON a.student_id = t4.studentId) T GROUP BY "校董id", "校董姓名", "服务商id", "服务商姓名", "学生姓名", "学生系统账号", "ETP大赛状态", "队伍名称") CT

SELECT  "登录日期" ,  sum("登录人数") AS "sum(登录人数)",sum("参赛人数") AS "sum(参赛人数)" FROM (select  loginday as "登录日期" ,loginnum as "登录人数" ,racenum as "参赛人数"  from hive.dwm.dwm_etc_race_action) T GROUP BY "登录日期" ORDER BY "登录日期" asc

select count(distinct a.user_id) as enter_num,
count(distinct b.user_id)as quit_num,
a.point_min
from (
SELECT cast(json_extract(replace(sourcedata,'$',''),'$.user_id') as decimal(20,0)) AS user_id,
          concat(substr(format_datetime(from_unixtime(cast(json_extract(replace(sourcedata,'$',''),'$.time') as decimal(20,0))/1000),'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm'),1,15),'0') AS point_min
   FROM hive.ods_point.point_en_etpdasai_cocos_url_enter_topic where dt=cast(current_date as varchar)
   )a
   left join
   (
   SELECT cast(json_extract(replace(sourcedata,'$',''),'$.user_id') as decimal(20,0)) AS user_id,
          concat(substr(format_datetime(from_unixtime(cast(json_extract(replace(sourcedata,'$',''),'$.time') as decimal(20,0))/1000),'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm'),1,15),'0') AS point_min
   FROM hive.ods_point.point_en_etpdasai_cocos_url_quit_topic where dt=cast(current_date as varchar)
   
   )b on a.point_min=b.point_min
   group by a.point_min
   order by a.point_min

SELECT  "队伍人数","报名情况" ,  sum("队伍数量") AS "sum(队伍数量)",sum("学生数量") AS "sum(学生数量)" FROM (select  team_sum as "队伍人数" ,type as "报名情况" ,team_num as "队伍数量" ,num * jishu as "学生数量" from(select 	case when num>10 then 0 else num end as team_sum  	,'报名成功' as type  	,count(teamid) as team_num 	,case when count(teamid)=0 then 1 else count(teamid) end as  jishu 	,a.num as num from( 	select  		teamId 		,count(studentId) as num 	from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player 	where registrationStatus=1 	and dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	group by 1 	)a group by 1,5 )b UNION select 	team_sum as "队伍人数" 	,type as "报名情况" 	,team_num as "队伍数量" 	,num * jishu as "学生数量" from( select 	case when num>10 then 0 else num end as team_sum 	,'未报名成功' as type  	,count(teamid) as team_num 	,case when count(teamid)=0 then 1 else count(teamid) end  as jishu 	,a.num as num from( 	select  		teamId 		,count(studentId) as num 	from hive.ods_english_etp_race.ods_etp_race_player 	where registrationStatus=0 	and dt = date_format(date_add( 'day' ,-1, current_timestamp),'%Y-%m-%d') 	group by 1 )a group by 1,5 )b order by 1) T GROUP BY "队伍人数","报名情况" ORDER BY "队伍人数" asc
